OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FShowers in the northwest on Tuesday,
OL,7,Fand perhaps west Cornwall on
OL,8,FWednesday. Otherwise dry with some
OL,9,Fsunshine. Strong easterly winds mid
OL,10,Fweek, though warming up across the
OL,11,Fsouth and west.
